videos.description: Kentucky's Reid Travis rolls to the basket and rises for a nice two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Travis rises for nice two-handed slam

videos.description: Kentucky's Ashton Hagans lobs it to PJ  Washington who throws down a nasty two-handed slam over a Louisville defender.
videos.headline: Washington throws down vicious alley-oop slam

videos.description: Kentucky shows off its hustle as they fight for the offensive rebound and kick it to Jemarl Baker who drains a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Kentucky's hustle leads to open 3-pointer

videos.description: Louisville's Christian Cunningham launches it high to Steven Enoch who finishes it with a sweet two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Enoch skies for sweet finish

videos.description: Louisville's Jordan Nwora gets free in transition and throws down a monster one-handed slam at the end of the half.
videos.headline: Nwora slams home monster dunk at buzzer

videos.description: Kentucky gets out on the break as PJ Washington feeds Keldon Johnson for a viscous alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Washington hits Johnson for emphatic slam
